  "text": "Early studies, dating back to the 1940s, found evidence of unstable or poor alpha rhythm in alcoholics [CITATION_1] , indicating a poor capacity for relaxation. Finn & Justus [CITATION_2] reported reduced alpha power in the children of alcoholics.",
